                <description>瞎扯 · 是什么让你们突然不想减肥了？ 知乎日报 查看知乎原文 Q：是什么让你们突然不想减肥了？ @tommstein：我老公这样的屌丝不配拥有太漂亮的媳妇！ Q： 最冷的冷知识有什么？ @开江鱼gty ：植物大战僵尸，这个巨人僵尸后面背一个小僵尸，他们的关系是什么？ 肯定很多人说他们是父子，其实他们是哥俩而且小的那个还是大哥(๑❛ᴗ❛๑) Q：尼罗鳄和虎鲸打起来谁赢? @光磁射线：虎鲸:再给我吃…</description>
                <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="main-img" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-96cd49294c50c5e43b6d7f0b7846fbe8.jpg?source=8673f162" style="max-width:100%; border-radius: 8px;"></div><div class="main-wrap content-wrap">
<div class="headline">

<div class="img-place-holder"></div>



</div>

<div class="content-inner">




<div class="question">
<h2 class="question-title">瞎扯 · 是什么让你们突然不想减肥了？</h2>

<div class="answer">

<div class="meta">
<img class="avatar" src="https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-fc734cfcc0b308e24640f9b5a2d2316d_l.jpg?source=8673f162">
<span class="author">知乎日报</span>
<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/None/answer/None" class="originUrl" hidden>查看知乎原文</a>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/310674916/answer/1997325189332100706" target="_blank">是什么让你们突然不想减肥了？</a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/abf1c5af8b6c1c502ed5ef6e514a5e53" target="_blank">@tommstein</a>：我老公这样的屌丝不配拥有太漂亮的媳妇！</div>
</blockquote>
<figure>
<div class="RichText-ConditionalImagePortal"><img class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-deea406f02b0e4a66123462ce9e33127_1440w.jpg" alt="" width="644"></div>
<figcaption></figcaption></figure>
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/648755666/answer/1999273733110663058" target="_blank"> 最冷的冷知识有什么？</a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/f1c9e6d777fc0ebcfb232c1508515614" target="_blank">@开江鱼gty</a> ：植物大战僵尸，这个<a class="RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1" href="https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=272811294&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%B7%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%83%B5%E5%B0%B8&amp;zhida_source=entity" target="_blank">巨人僵尸</a>后面背一个小僵尸，他们的关系是什么？</div>
肯定很多人说他们是父子，其实他们是哥俩<br>而且小的那个还是大哥(๑❛ᴗ❛๑)</blockquote>
<figure>
<div class="RichText-ConditionalImagePortal"><img class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3fe01c71f30760144cfae69cc95e1617_1440w.jpg" alt="" width="579"></div>
<figcaption></figcaption></figure>
<figure>
<div class="RichText-ConditionalImagePortal"><img class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" src="https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-aedb36a0f542cbd906f450d9ae614bc0_1440w.jpg" alt="" width="720"></div>
<figcaption></figcaption></figure>
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/2666647197/answer/1903628407088080515" target="_blank">尼罗鳄和</a><a class="RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1" href="https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=272811294&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E8%99%8E%E9%B2%B8&amp;zhida_source=entity" target="_blank">虎鲸</a>打起来谁赢? </p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/62e30f52c27c9a2b7a9ef8cb36565c38" target="_blank">@光磁射线</a>：虎鲸:再给我吃这种皮硬肉少的东西，把你肝挖出来 </div>
</blockquote>
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/590792394/answer/1989726841112633353" target="_blank"> 为什么昆虫长得都那么离谱？</a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/de5a8cac82c1edc8647640173b33b684" target="_blank">@火鸟</a> ：换个角度看，昆虫眼里的人类才是最恶心的：骨头埋在身体里面，肉体全部翻在外面，像剥了壳露出来的一滩血肉。</div>
</blockquote>
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/1941154755620611466/answer/1997004065318671556" target="_blank">钓鱼佬最接受不了什么？ </a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/111f6baf2774c534662d506cad853631" target="_blank">@老北1</a>：不顾老婆的威胁和恳求执意出去钓鱼，结果空军回家后被老婆肆意嘲笑。</div>
</blockquote>
<p><br class="Apple-interchange-newline"><br class="Apple-interchange-newline"></p>
</div>
</div>


